{
  "texts": [
    "Interviews' duration ranged between 15 to 85 minutes (mean = 41.24, SD = 20.97).",
    "Human participants were sampled using the criterion sampling strategy within pragmatic limits, i.e.",
    "having the diversity and breadth of the population in mind, including physical functioning level (NYHA class), ethnicity, and sex, please see the original report [32].",
    "Human participant recruitment has been reported previously, and qualitative data saturation was checked to ensure that a sufficient number of samples were recruited.",
    "We used a structured approach for determining saturation in theory-based interview studies, particularly those utilizing preestablished conceptual categories from existing theory, following methodology outlined by [50]."
  ]
}